{% schema %}
  {
    
    "name": "Section 9",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-607396651660739158 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/sheikhashadul/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_ARTICLE&editorId=607381796862034487&sectionId=607396651660739158)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggVnwn0wXbF_text","label":"ggVnwn0wXbF_text","default":"So If Your Skin Was Like A Sagging Fabric,<br>Progeline Doesn't Just Temporarily Tighten The Surface... It Actually Reinforces The Entire<br>Structure From Within, Creating A Naturally Lifted, Youthful Appearance That Lasts!"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBjyeY1Gu8_text","label":"ggBjyeY1Gu8_text","default":"<p>So that's what Progeline can do on a scientific level. But what does all that mean for you?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9LGWOie33_text","label":"gg9LGWOie33_text","default":"<p>Well, when you look at studies on the effects of Progeline, you quickly realize how incredible this compound is...and the profound effect it can have on your appearance, your confidence, and your overall youthfulness.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggihDpBngo7_text","label":"ggihDpBngo7_text","default":"<p>In a landmark study, 23 women ages 34 to 78 who were struggling with aging skin, sagging, and wrinkles had their results compared with younger women.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3VSjJQOPI_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg3VSjJQOPI_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s8img1_771e96a4-df37-43d1-8ba2-b55441681238.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7sUn2GE4V_text","label":"gg7sUn2GE4V_text","default":"<p>The women using Progeline ALL had significantly improved skin appearance.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZaV5bfU0y_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggZaV5bfU0y_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s8img1_771e96a4-df37-43d1-8ba2-b55441681238.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNTa89fW7f_text","label":"ggNTa89fW7f_text","default":"<p>And the women without Progeline continued to show signs of aging.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWOihVu22A_text","label":"ggWOihVu22A_text","default":"<p><strong>Progeline </strong>was the difference between youthful and aging skin.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjOtLjtIhS_text","label":"ggjOtLjtIhS_text","default":"<p><strong>This confirms separate research that Progeline could help reduce visible signs of aging by up to 22%.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglbuUOdAF2_text","label":"gglbuUOdAF2_text","default":"<p>But it doesn't end there.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggShNAgHsve_text","label":"ggShNAgHsve_text","default":"<p>In 2003, French scientists published their groundbreaking study showing that the aging protein Progerin not only causes wrinkles... <strong>it affects our skin's entire structure.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBHKMjGVRp_text","label":"ggBHKMjGVRp_text","default":"<p>So having reduced Progerin levels means you have the skin structure of someone much younger (whether you actually are or not!)</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-0VV79aIC_text","label":"gg-0VV79aIC_text","default":"<p>If it sounds incredible that all of this is associated with less Progerin and more Progeline in your skin, believe me, it is!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggySNzlvmsX_text","label":"ggySNzlvmsX_text","default":"<p>But it's not surprising when you remember what's happening in the average woman's skin...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2Q6xbi7Iw_text","label":"gg2Q6xbi7Iw_text","default":"<p>We've been exposed to things that increase Progerin dramatically…including not just UV rays, but also environmental toxins, stress, and poor skincare products...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdTWOEI5hU_text","label":"ggdTWOEI5hU_text","default":"<p>We've been exposed to things that increase&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDd0wYZ-zh_text","label":"ggDd0wYZ-zh_text","default":"<p>Progerin dramatically…including not just UV&nbsp;rays,</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg39edkJTii_text","label":"gg39edkJTii_text","default":"<p>&nbsp;but also environmental toxins, stress, and poor skincare products...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggi8E3iq_sC_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggi8E3iq_sC_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s8img2.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUDwaLwwy4_text","label":"ggUDwaLwwy4_text","default":"<p>And we use products with ingredients far too often that actually accelerate aging... even though studies show every chemical-laden product you use damages your skin for years.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHsR1UIaF4_text","label":"ggHsR1UIaF4_text","default":"<p>When your skin is weak, these compounds create havoc on our appearance.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggN7N46FGDT_text","label":"ggN7N46FGDT_text","default":"<p>When your skin is weak, these compounds create havoc on our appearance.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjUpkqTDMa_text","label":"ggjUpkqTDMa_text","default":"<p>But Progeline fixes the damage.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAYU4T6yQW_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggAYU4T6yQW_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s8img3.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqDQhm6Bdn_text","label":"ggqDQhm6Bdn_text","default":"<p><strong>And the more you have of it, the better you're going to look.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIH6pz3-Nk_text","label":"ggIH6pz3-Nk_text","default":"<p>I can tell you, both as a doctor and from treating thousands of patients, I now consider Progeline to be one of – if not THE – most important youth-boosting compounds for aging skin.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnAaj4q7OQ_text","label":"ggnAaj4q7OQ_text","default":"<p>In fact, there is almost no aspect of your appearance that age-fighting compounds don't play a massive role in.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1N3-AKnLQ_text","label":"gg1N3-AKnLQ_text","default":"<p><strong>The most important one?</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6l30epRlK_text","label":"gg6l30epRlK_text","default":"<p><strong>You guessed it, how much Progeline you have in your skin.</strong></p>"}],
